title: Ebro In The Morning - Ray J In Mar-A-Lago, Into the Metaverse + The Word "Woke"
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 1/27/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez, and the crew are in the studio - Ebro takes issue with the co-opting of the word "woke."

The crew talks about virtual reality, Ray J and Trump's meeting, and the gurus give advice! All that and more on Ebro In The Morning!
